<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>PESTLE Analysis — UK Business</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Figtree:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

body {
  font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, sans-serif;
  min-height: 100vh;
  background: #000;
  color: #fff;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

.bg {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: 0;
  background: #060608;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.bg-orb {
  position: absolute;
  border-radius: 50%;
  filter: blur(90px);
  opacity: 0.45;
  animation: drift linear infinite;
}

.bg-orb-1 {
  width: 700px; height: 700px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, #3d2fa0, transparent 70%);
  top: -200px; left: -150px;
  animation-duration: 28s;
}
.bg-orb-2 {
  width: 600px; height: 600px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, #0a4fa6, transparent 70%);
  top: 20%; right: -100px;
  animation-duration: 22s;
  animation-delay: -8s;
}
.bg-orb-3 {
  width: 500px; height: 500px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, #1a7a3a, transparent 70%);
  bottom: 5%; left: 20%;
  animation-duration: 32s;
  animation-delay: -15s;
}
.bg-orb-4 {
  width: 400px; height: 400px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, #7a1a4a, transparent 70%);
  bottom: 20%; right: 10%;
  animation-duration: 26s;
  animation-delay: -4s;
}

@keyframes drift {
  0%   { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); }
  33%  { transform: translate(40px, -30px) scale(1.05); }
  66%  { transform: translate(-20px, 40px) scale(0.97); }
  100% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); }
}

.page {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  max-width: 1120px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 80px 24px 100px;
}

header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 72px;
}

.eyebrow {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}

h1 {
  font-size: clamp(42px, 6vw, 72px);
  font-weight: 300;
  letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  line-height: 1;
  background: linear-gradient(160deg, #fff 30%, rgba(255,255,255,0.45));
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.subtitle {
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
  max-width: 440px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  line-height: 1.6;
  letter-spacing: 0.01em;
}

.grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 14px;
}

@media (max-width: 800px) { .grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); } }
@media (max-width: 520px) { .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

.card {
  position: relative;
  border-radius: 24px;
  padding: 26px 24px 28px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.055);
  backdrop-filter: blur(40px) saturate(180%);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(40px) saturate(180%);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(.25,.8,.25,1), background 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
}

.card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  border-radius: 24px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.08) 0%, transparent 60%);
  pointer-events: none;
}

.card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.005);
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
}

.card-shine {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 16px; right: 16px;
  height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.35), transparent);
}

.card-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 13px;
  margin-bottom: 22px;
}

.badge {
  width: 38px; height: 38px;
  border-radius: 11px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
}

.card-title {
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}
.card-sub {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
  letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  margin-top: 2px;
}

.factors { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }

.factor { padding: 13px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07); }
.factor:last-child { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }
.factor:first-child { padding-top: 0; }

.factor-name {
  font-size: 12.5px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
  margin-bottom: 4px;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}
.factor-desc {
  font-size: 11.5px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.38);
  line-height: 1.55;
  font-weight: 400;
}

.card-p .badge { background: rgba(88,86,214,0.25); color: #a89ef5; }
.card-e .badge { background: rgba(52,199,89,0.2); color: #5de087; }
.card-s .badge { background: rgba(255,159,10,0.2); color: #ffbf52; }
.card-t .badge { background: rgba(0,122,255,0.2); color: #5aadff; }
.card-l .badge { background: rgba(255,59,48,0.2); color: #ff7b73; }
.card-env .badge { background: rgba(48,209,88,0.2); color: #52e87a; }

footer {
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 60px;
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="bg">
  <div class="bg-orb bg-orb-1"></div>
  <div class="bg-orb bg-orb-2"></div>
  <div class="bg-orb bg-orb-3"></div>
  <div class="bg-orb bg-orb-4"></div>
</div>

<div class="page">

  <header>
    <p class="eyebrow">Business Analysis Framework</p>
    <h1>PESTLE Analysis</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Key external factors affecting UK businesses — applicable across all sectors.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="grid">

    <div class="card card-p">
      <div class="card-shine"></div>
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="badge">P</div>
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Political</div>
          <div class="card-sub">Government &amp; policy</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <ul class="factors">
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">Post-Brexit trade rules</div><div class="factor-desc">New customs checks and import/export costs push up prices and complicate supply chains.</div></li>
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">Government spending cuts</div><div class="factor-desc">Austerity policies reduce public sector contracts and consumer confidence.</div></li>
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">National Living Wage rises</div><div class="factor-desc">Government-mandated annual increases directly raise labour costs for all employers.</div></li>
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">Corporation tax at 25%</div><div class="factor-desc">Raised in 2023, reducing post-tax profits for businesses of all sizes.</div></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card card-e">
      <div class="card-shine"></div>
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="badge">E</div>
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Economic</div>
          <div class="card-sub">Macro &amp; market conditions</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <ul class="factors">
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">High UK inflation (CPI)</div><div class="factor-desc">Drove up costs of materials, energy and wages significantly since 2022.</div></li>
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">Bank of England interest rates</div><div class="factor-desc">Higher rates increase borrowing costs, discouraging investment and expansion.</div></li>
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">Cost of living crisis</div><div class="factor-desc">Squeezed consumer disposable income reduces demand for non-essential goods and services.</div></li>
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">Weak pound sterling</div><div class="factor-desc">Makes imports more expensive, raising costs for businesses sourcing from abroad.</div></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card card-s">
      <div class="card-shine"></div>
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="badge">S</div>
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Social</div>
          <div class="card-sub">Demographics &amp; culture</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <ul class="factors">
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">Ageing UK population</div><div class="factor-desc">Over-65s are the fastest-growing demographic, shifting demand and shrinking the workforce.</div></li>
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">Rise of ethical consumerism</div><div class="factor-desc">UK consumers increasingly choose sustainable or ethically sourced brands.</div></li>
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">Remote/hybrid work culture</div><div class="factor-desc">Reduced demand for office space and commuter services; changed employee expectations.</div></li>
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">Mental health awareness</div><div class="factor-desc">Growing pressure on employers to invest in staff wellbeing, increasing HR costs.</div></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card card-t">
      <div class="card-shine"></div>
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="badge">T</div>
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Technological</div>
          <div class="card-sub">Innovation &amp; disruption</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <ul class="factors">
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">AI &amp; automation</div><div class="factor-desc">Cutting labour costs and improving efficiency, but threatening job displacement.</div></li>
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">Growth of e-commerce</div><div class="factor-desc">UK is one of Europe's largest online markets — businesses must adapt or lose share.</div></li>
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">Cybersecurity threats</div><div class="factor-desc">Rising data breaches expose businesses to UK GDPR fines and reputational damage.</div></li>
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">Cloud computing</div><div class="factor-desc">Lowers IT costs but creates dependency on third-party providers and connectivity.</div></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card card-l">
      <div class="card-shine"></div>
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="badge">L</div>
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Legal</div>
          <div class="card-sub">Compliance &amp; legislation</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <ul class="factors">
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">UK GDPR</div><div class="factor-desc">Non-compliance risks fines up to £17.5m or 4% of annual global turnover.</div></li>
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">Employment law</div><div class="factor-desc">Unfair dismissal, redundancy pay and workers' rights are tightly regulated.</div></li>
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">Health &amp; Safety at Work Act 1974</div><div class="factor-desc">Legal duty of care to employees; breaches can result in prosecution and unlimited fines.</div></li>
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">Consumer Rights Act 2015</div><div class="factor-desc">Goods and services must be fit for purpose — creates liability for all UK businesses.</div></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card card-env">
      <div class="card-shine"></div>
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="badge">E</div>
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Environmental</div>
          <div class="card-sub">Sustainability &amp; climate</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <ul class="factors">
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">UK Net Zero 2050 target</div><div class="factor-desc">Government pressure to cut emissions affects operations and reporting obligations.</div></li>
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">Energy costs</div><div class="factor-desc">UK energy prices spiked post-2022; remain a major overhead for most businesses.</div></li>
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">Plastic Packaging Tax</div><div class="factor-desc">£210.83 per tonne on packaging with under 30% recycled content, raising production costs.</div></li>
        <li class="factor"><div class="factor-name">Extreme weather risk</div><div class="factor-desc">Flooding and heatwaves increasingly disrupt UK supply chains, premises and logistics.</div></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>

  <footer>UK Generic PESTLE &nbsp;·&nbsp; All factors applicable across sectors</footer>

</div>
</body>
</html>
